“In Lille, I’m there all year round, which is not the case with Belgium.”
“I have to take my marks.”
Held against Romania on Friday night in preparation for this match against France, Hazard comes to Saint-Denis to finally "shine".
Without forgetting the notion of "pleasure".
Les Bleus, he has encouraged them since the age of 7 and the victorious campaigns of 1998 and 2000.
